This is the first release of the GRIME Map Viewer.

Version 1.0	- 01 Dec 1995
		  Internal Beta Release.

Version 1.1	- 11 Feb 1996
		  Initial Release. Minor bug fix to command line options.
		  File size is slightly smaller. :)

The  automatic  scrolling  isn't  brilliant, I hope to implement this option
better  in  the future.  I also would like to put in the option for printing
out the map as graphics. Also preferences via tooltypes would be good. Any
other ideas?

